                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <div class="accordion-header">Experience</div>
                    <div class="accordion-content">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Even as a student, you likely have experience that's worth including. This can include internships, part-time jobs, volunteer work, and significant academic projects.</p>
                            
                            <h4>How to Structure Each Entry:</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Position Title:</strong> Marketing Intern</li>
                                <li><strong>Organization Name:</strong> XYZ Company</li>
                                <li><strong>Location:</strong> Mumbai, India</li>
                                <li><strong>Dates:</strong> June 2022 - August 2022</li>
                                <li><strong>Accomplishments:</strong> 3-5 bullet points describing what you achieved</li>
                            </ul>
                            
                            <div class="tip">
                                <h4>Use the PAR Method for Bullet Points</h4>
                                <p><strong>P</strong>roblem: What challenge did you face?<br>
                                <strong>A</strong>ction: What did you do about it?<br>
                                <strong>R</strong>esult: What was the positive outcome?</p>
                            </div>
                            
