Marketing Intern                                                  June 2022 - August 2022
Digital Marketers Inc., Bangalore, India
• Created and scheduled content for social media platforms, increasing engagement by 35% over 3 months
• Analyzed campaign performance using Google Analytics, identifying key trends that informed strategy adjustments
• Collaborated with a team of 5 to develop and execute a product launch campaign that generated ₹3.5 lakhs in sales
• Designed promotional materials using Canva and Adobe Photoshop for both digital and print distribution
